These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: onion, cherry, asparagus
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, baking
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, dressmaker, dancer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, pop, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, american, mexican
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, baseball, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is the american##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the dancer##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the mexican and the person drinking juice##2
 4. the fan of pop is on the left of the canadian##1
 5. the dressmaker is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is the canadian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the dressmaker##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | juice    | almond-milk   | cola           |
| Food          | cherry       | asparagus    | onion         |
| Hobby         | dancing    | baking  | cooking        |
| Job           | security-guard | dressmaker   | dancer      |
| Music-Genre   | pop        | hip-hop    | reggae       |
| Nationality   | american     | canadian  | mexican       |
| Sport         | soccer     | baseball | skateboarding |

