There 3 different types of food: tomato, banana, pineapple
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, time-travel, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, folk, techno
There are 3 different nationalities: french, mexican, canadian
3 different pets are kept: goat, hamster, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, swimming, soccer
 1. the owner of the snake is the mexican##1
 2. the owner of the snake is the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking milk##2
 5. the canadian is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of salsa##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person eating tomato is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the fan of techno##1
10. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | milk   | tea    | mirinda         |
| Food          | tomato    | banana | pineapple          |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | superhero  | time-travel     |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | folk      | salsa         |
| Nationality   | canadian      | mexican   | french    |
| Pet           | goat        | snake      | hamster         |
