The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, water-polo, rugby
 1. the person eating strawberry is the owner of the rat##1
 2. the colombian is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating grapefruit##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the rat##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the american and the fan of rock##2
 8. the american is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
11. the american is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | grapefruit      | strawberry      | avocado      |
