 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the fan of reggae##2
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the owner of the lizard##2
 7. the person driving the boat is between the person eating pumpkin and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 8. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of house##1
 9. the electrician is on the right of the fan of house##1
10. the dancer is the person eating pumpkin##1

