11. the person driving the ship is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk      | 7up      |
| Hobby         | board-games     | chess     | photography  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | superhero  | comedy |
| Nationality   | japanese  | argentine     | brazilian |
| Pet           | cat        | horse | chinchilla     |
| Sport         | golf    | tennis | surfing   |
| Transport     | airplane        | trike        | ship   |

