.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, sprite
There 3 different types of food: radish, lime, avocado
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, board-games, camping
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, engineer, freelancer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, soy-milksy, spy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, handball, baseball
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, bike, trike
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the freelancer##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
3. the person eating lime is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person watching drama movies and the engineer##2
5. the person eating avocado is between the freelancer and the person who's hobby is camping##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
9. the person watching soy-milksy movies is on the left of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | almond-milk      | sprite       |
