| Hobby         | camping    | video-games     | board-games     |
| Job           | engineer    | firefighter | freelancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | soy-milksy    | spy    | drama       |
| Sport         | baseball | skiing      | handball    |
| Transport     | bike       | tram | trike |

