There 3 different types of food: mango, plum, pear
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, magic-tricks
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, adventure, horror
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, r&b, country
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, sailing
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, van, roller
1. the person driving the van is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person eating plum is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person eating pear is on the right of the fan of country##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
8. the person driving the subway is the person watching horror movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
