.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, cola, sprite
There 3 different types of food: lemon, pomegranate, apricot
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, accountant, teacher
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, dutch, chinese
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, ferret
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting, swimming
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, airplane
1. the person drinking water is the person eating apricot##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the writer is between the person drinking sprite and the owner of the ferret##2
4. the thai is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
7. the accountant is the person eating lemon##1
8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the dutch is between the person eating lemon and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | cola    | water       | sprite      |
| Food          | lemon   | apricot   | pomegranate  |
| Job           | accountant  | writer | teacher    |
| Nationality   | thai   | dutch     | chinese  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig        | goldfish |
| Sport         | weightlifting | water-polo   | swimming  |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | airplane     | quad-bike      |

 